- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is a relevant category as the k-induction algorithm is a formal verification technique that relies on automata theory.
- cs.ET (Emerging Technologies) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper proposes a novel approach to improve the efficiency of the k-induction algorithm, which could be considered an emerging technology in the field of formal verification.
